sourceQuestion:
Which of the following are regular sets?
I.   {a^(2m) | n >= 2, m >= 0}
II.  {a^(n^2) | n >= 0}
III. {a^(mn) | m >= 1, n >= 1}
IV.  {a^(n!) | n >= 0}

A. I and IV only
B. I and III only
C. I only
D. IV only

